title: Pre-match anxiety discussion
content: Athlete expressed concerns about upcoming championship match. Discussed breathing techniques and visualization exercises. Recommended continued practice of mindfulness techniques.

title: Team communication issues
content: Athlete reported feeling isolated from team during training. Discussed strategies for improving communication with teammates and coaching staff. Suggested team-building activities.

title: Post-injury psychological support
content: Athlete struggling with confidence after recent injury. Working on mental resilience and positive self-talk. Progress noted in acceptance of current limitations.

title: Season goals and motivation
content: Reviewed season objectives and personal development goals. Athlete shows strong intrinsic motivation. Discussed strategies for maintaining focus during challenging periods.

title: Sleep quality concerns
content: Athlete reporting poor sleep quality affecting training performance. Discussed sleep hygiene practices and relaxation techniques. Recommended sleep tracking app.

title: Media pressure handling
content: Athlete feeling overwhelmed by media attention and public expectations. Discussed strategies for managing external pressure and maintaining focus on performance.

title: Confidence restoration session
content: Working on rebuilding confidence after recent performance dip. Focused on positive self-talk and visualization of successful performances. Good progress shown.

title: Concentration training
content: Athlete struggling with maintaining focus during long training sessions. Introduced concentration exercises and mindfulness techniques. Practice recommended.
